  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Albania Kapshtica Reception Facilitiy</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project will support border and migration management capabilities of Albania, including identification/registration of migrants crossing the border in an irregular manner, identify vulnerabilities and strengthen the capacity to countering migrant smuggling and human trafficking in full respect of the rule of law and fundamental rights. The project will take place in Albania, focusing in the south-eastern border with Greece where the migrants and refugees enter Albania. Considering the current flows and their patterns the Border Crossing Point (BCP) of Kapshtica is a priority.</narrative>
  </description>
